1. *Svemira* ima bezbroj, a mi još uvek istražujemo samo mali deo. (There are countless *universes*, and we are still exploring only a small part of them.)
2. Učenje o *svemiru* može biti fascinantno i za decu i za odrasle. (Studying the *cosmos* can be fascinating for both children and adults.)
3. *Svemirski* letovi postaju sve učestaliji u poslednje vreme. (Space flights are becoming increasingly common lately.)
4. Naša zemlja se nalazi u *svemirskom* prostoru. (Our planet is located in *space*.)
5. *Svemirskim* teleskopom možemo posmatrati daleke planete i galaksije. (With a *space* telescope, we can observe distant planets and galaxies.)
6. *Svemiru* je potrebno mnogo istraživanja kako bismo shvatili njegove tajne. (A lot of research is needed to understand the secrets of the *universe*.)
7. Naučnici su otkrili mnoge zanimljive pojave u *svemiru*. (Scientists have discovered many interesting phenomena in the *cosmos*.)
8. Planiramo da pošaljemo novu misiju u *svemir* sledeće godine. (We are planning to send a new space mission next year.)
9. *Svemirska* stanica orbitira oko Zemlje već nekoliko godina. (The *space* station has been orbiting around the Earth for several years.)
10. Zbog zagađenja, *svemir* postaje sve manje prijateljsko mesto za život. (Due to pollution, *space* is becoming an increasingly unfriendly place for living.)